Service,Recommended DB,Reason
User Management,PostgreSQL,Structured data, relational queries, and integrity requirements (e.g., unique email, relationships).
AI/Content Generation,MongoDB,Semi-structured or unstructured data with nested sections.
Third-Party Data Integration,MongoDB,Varying schemas for fetched data from external APIs.
File Generation,PostgreSQL,Metadata for files is highly structured and linked to users.
Notification Service,MongoDB,Flexible schema for different notification types (e.g., email, push).
Payment Service,PostgreSQL,Transactional data requiring consistency and relationships.
Report Customization,MongoDB,User-specific and flexible customization options.
Analytics Service,MongoDB,Event-driven, time-series data with high write throughput.
Template Management,PostgreSQL,Structured templates reusable across users, requiring categorization and versioning.
